8-10-26T02:31:33.000Z","msg":"任你up 啦"},{"pid":"738fb90859f3439dab3806bdaa03a5ae1395933f","tid":876760,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T02:31:43.000Z","msg":"原來上唔到網就叫hang機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d0c77d4917a12a992d2e84d80d98bc22949e87d","tid":876760,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T02:33:45.000Z","msg":"我小學果陣唔知點樣張櫈zip住左條lan線再一拖<br />\n結果好彩lan 線冇斷 但更不幸係成部主機跌落地"},{"pid":"1f287d8066de23c255f1871ccf2bc5454290789f","tid":876760,"uid":155373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b80c0ae0abd427a488b54f8b71f1a81166dca59","tid":876760,"uid":35014,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T00:43:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T02:45:47.000Z","msg":"條cctv片應該做咗手腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊有可能咁大力"},{"pid":"521e5ed9a7828d4023108ebe5e0c2125101eea03","tid":876760,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T02:49:12.000Z","msg":"最後冇拎到條線已經俾人帶走<br />\n咁點樣自殺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128b026b17dc71d9b51050adf0ef538b8e8741a8","tid":876760,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T02:49:45.000Z","msg":"個pc仔不回答？算唔算藐視法庭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be98c13ffd38ad322068f79a1d01702cd1597597","tid":876760,"uid":3117,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"241cceb947d30aaed50e419255ae79db0db1929d","tid":876760,"uid":340,"like":5,"dislike":24,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T00:51:20.000Z","msg":"連登仔又炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T02:52:30.000Z","msg":"炒你老母？"},{"pid":"bfb58c340caba